@startuml UC_29_Manage_Platform
title UC-29: Manage Platform

|Admin|
start
:(1) Open the admin portal;
:(2) Log in with admin credentials;

|System|
:(3) Validate admin authentication;
:(4) Issue admin access and refresh tokens;
:(5) Allow access to the dashboard and admin tools;

|Admin|
:(6) Log out when finished;

|System|
:(7) Revoke the active admin session;
:(8) Confirm logout;

stop
@enduml
